-- Create date: <9/17/2008>
-- Description:	<Store Procedure for ECF50 Sale Report v1>
-- =============================================
-- Modifier:		<Jooeun Lee>
-- Modified date:	<1/23/2012>
-- Description:		<Fixed bug counting duplicate line items after creating a return (ECF ver. 5.2.571)>
-- =============================================
